m\" style=\"color:#1a56a0;\">info@dotcomweavers.com</a> &nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.dotcomweavers.com\" style=\"color:#1a56a0;\">www.dotcomweavers.com</a></p></div>{{ $('For Each Client').item.json.manual_attachment === 'yes' ? '<br><p style=\"color:#b45309;background:#fef3c7;padding:12px;border-left:4px solid #b45309;margin:16px 0 0;\"><strong>⚠️ REMINDER:</strong> Manually attach timesheet before sending.</p>' : '' }}</div>",
